HEADWORD: Securement
<hw>Se*cure"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
securing; protection.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Society condemns the <qex>securement</qex> in all cases of
perpetual protection by means of perpetual imprisonment.</q> <rj><qau>C.
A. Ives.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Secureness</ent>⟦br⟧
